---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 76
By: Israel Baal Shern
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=Pride
---
It is in respect to sinners that God designates Himself (in the Torah) as ‘He
who dwells in the midst of their impurities.’ But as our sages (of the
Talmud) teach, God says concerning the person of pride： ‘I and he cannot live
together in the world.’
